Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User
PassCmd "emacs --batch -l ~/.emacs -f email-password"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs PLAIN

IMAPStore gmail
Account gmail

MaildirStore local
Path ~/mail/
Inbox ~/mail/INBOX/

Channel gmail-default
Master :gmail:
Slave :local:

Channel gmail-archive
Master :gmail:"[Google Mail]/All Mail"
Slave :local:archive

Channel gmail-drafts
Master :gmail:"[Google Mail]/Drafts"
Slave :local:drafts

Channel gmail-sent
Master :gmail:"[Google Mail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :local:sent

Channel gmail-spam
Master :gmail:"[Google Mail]/Spam"
Slave :local:spam

Channel gmail-trash
Master :gmail:"[Google Mail]/Bin"
Slave :local:trash

Group default
Channel gmail-default
Channel gmail-archive
Channel gmail-drafts
Channel gmail-sent
Channel gmail-spam
Channel gmail-trash

